{"tid":2068830,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"蘇官曾指7.21白衣人「勇敢面對」","createTime":"2020-06-18T03:26:37.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-18T05:17:55.000Z","uid":25558,"like":11,"dislike":29,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"3d5323d95996fa2bd6c5904382f81d0361a29a6a","tid":2068830,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T03:26:37.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200618/3MYJ6UJA2QTA4NIGAS5DTF2KVE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200618%2F3MYJ6UJA2QTA4NIGAS5DTF2KVE%2F&d=u0uYB5UElWTGJsHKTdw4weBrFmK%2FfjgW9YhWFGnkYF4%3D&h=d7597cce\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200618%2F3MYJ6UJA2QTA4NIGAS5DTF2KVE%2F&h=3797d55a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200618/3MYJ6UJA2QTA4NIGAS5DTF2KVE/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n蘇官曾指7.21白衣人「勇敢面對」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/WPFE7K6LQCPK7BCBNHBNR5VMZE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FWPFE7K6LQCPK7BCBNHBNR5VMZE.jpg&h=d04f406c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n裁判官蘇文隆<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】裁判官蘇文隆過去審案的言論或決定不時惹起關注，例如7.21元朗白衣人無差別襲擊市民事件的燒烤場東主，他雖指鐵證如山，但稱東主勇敢面對，與警方保持聯絡，沒有潛逃迹象，故批准保釋。他亦試過判涉用馬騮試槍的休班警無罪，更判涉毒交通警感化。<br />\n<br />\n7.21事件一周後，市民7.27在元朗示威，抗議白衣人無差別襲擊市民以及「警黑勾結」，有四名青年因涉藏有氣槍及瑞士軍刀等物品被拘控。案件首次提訊時蘇官指四人攜有的工具可用作武器，他們在場出現目的「呼之欲出」，不准保釋。其中一名19歲青年還柙一周後成功向高院取得保釋，後來控方更撤銷起訴他。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n判藏毒交警感化<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：社福界斥打壓為實 憂開壞先例<br />\n<br />\n另外，蘇官曾處理涉及紀律部隊人員犯法的案件，有休班警深夜時分到「馬騮山」試槍，懲教員撞破他以馬騮做活靶開10槍。蘇官認為「除非啲馬騮着咗螢光衫」，否則在漆黑草叢難以辨別，質疑尖叫聲有可能來自野豬、山貓或馬騮，裁定休班警狩獵和虐待馬騮罪名不成立。<br />\n<br />\n亦有交通警在羅湖過關時被搜出身藏偉哥、冰毒等，蘇官。。。。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n■記者戴國輝"},{"pid":"fbb819fedfcff9317e919ed2facce872cadb7c6b","tid":2068830,"uid":77092,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T03:29:12.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a283356baec7ac59fd025727a9aa9c0c92239f5e","tid":2068830,"uid":265839,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T03:30:41.000Z","msg":"黑官"},{"pid":"00d2ff1a764c269a5be385f22effa4e1599485b3","tid":2068830,"uid":50740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T03:31:06.000Z","msg":"黑官"},{"pid":"73565e737f2a3ef188a3d2ce44d2a0707c33cf9c","tid":2068830,"uid":159920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T03:31:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5daf93912132da8694e0b708917e8bf4251d7341","tid":2068830,"uid":6537,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T03:33:09.000Z","msg":"認撚住佢個樣，咪撚出街啊"},{"pid":"073c06983b5332aced437db8f8969c4872fc837a","tid":2068830,"uid":60434,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"5daf93912132da8694e0b708917e8bf4251d7341","tid":2068830,"uid":6537,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T03:33:09.000Z","msg":"認撚住佢個樣，咪撚出街啊"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T03:33:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e47e693a1cd0e7011ecc31ef1abd7e5aa095a5c","tid":2068830,"uid":70345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T03:34:20.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"75a25ea8e013b0d72342a2ccf48df026a4b4fa9a","tid":2068830,"uid":184726,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T03:34:41.000Z","msg":"個樣都成個支那仔咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"afdfb106dccf4587237073081a8fc04e17636da0","tid":2068830,"uid":109629,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T03:35:14.000Z","msg":"咁撚樣衰 真係好易認"},{"pid":"8876ae7a4971a8549f8fb73e87d8d1d22f29cac2","tid":2068830,"uid":470